            <br>
            <p class="card-text ">
              <p>I am passionate about math and helping students learn.
                <br>
                Here are few facts about who I am:
              </p>
              <ul class="about-list">
                <li>Certified Math teacher</li>
                <li>Tutoring since 2006</li>
                <li>Enjoy teaching Math</li>
                <br>
                <ion-icon name="calculator" style="font-size: 200px;"></ion-icon>
                <br>
                <li>When not tutoring, I love spending time with my children, working on sudoku puzzles,
                   and eating chocolate.
                <li>
              </ul>
            </p>
          </section>
        </section>
        <!-- /.row -->
        <section class="row centered-form center-block text-center">
          <section class="container col-md-12 col-md-offset-1 border  rounded p-3 mb-2 bg-info text-white"">
            <h4 class="card-title">Need Tutoring?</h4>
            <% include ./partials/form.ejs %>
          </section>
        </section>
